nd bring you the very best WordPress ecommerce plugin possible.  To that end, I wanted to share with you what the next two big releases will be.  Next week, we&#8217;re hoping to finish wpStoreCart 2.3, which adds social media sharing, image galleries, and light boxes.  We will continue to release additional 2.3.x versions throughout May and June, all leading up to the big release of wpStoreCart 3 in late June (possibly July if there are delays.)  Full details are below:</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-723\"></span><br />\nWhat&#8217;s new in the upcoming wpStoreCart 2.3.x branch later this May:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Social media sharing of products (2.3.0)</li>\n<li>Optional lightbox for viewing product images (2.3.0)</li>\n<li>Image galleries with unlimited number of images per product (2.3.0)</li>\n<li>Customers will have the ability to sort products by Low Price, High Price, Newest, and Oldest (2.3.x)</li>\n<li>Tax options will be exposed (2.3.x)</li>\n<li>New Payment Failed page (2.3.x)</li>\n<li>Ability to delete and rename product uploads from the Download tab when editing a product (2.3.x)</li>\n</ul>\n<p />\n<br />\nWhat&#8217;s upcoming in wpStoreCart 3, coming June:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Customers can use filters to see products only from specific manufacturers </li>\n<li>New widgets added: manufacturers, payments accepted, fancy newest products, and fancy most popular </li>\n<li>Two new WordPress user roles: Customer and Merchant</li>\n<li>Product groups and multi-item packages.  Sell groups of your products together as a single product</li>\n<li>3 different cart styles, and multiple checkout styles configurable </li>\n<li>Video and audio players for mp3, flv, and more</li>\n<li>Optionally, user must accept a license agreement, terms of service, privacy policy, and other legal issues</li>\n<li>Bulk, multi-item discounts</li>\n<li>Payment Gateway API to create your own custom payment gateways</li>\n<li>Shipping Gateway API to create your own shipping service integration</li>\n<li>Temporary sale prices per product</li>\n<li>Percentage off sales for the entire store, specific categories, and/or individual products</li>\n<li>Redesigned admin panel, with more inline Ajax editing through out</li>\n<li>Coupons can now be limited to 1 or more uses only before they expire</li>\n<li>WPMU and BuddyPress support!</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"http://wpstorecart.com/announcing-wpstorecart-2-3-and-3-0/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n	\n		\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Sell Software With Serial Numbers Using WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 14 May 2011 03:05:54 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://wpstorecart.com/?p=658\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:479:\"With the release of wpStoreCart 2.2.9, you can now have wpStoreCart automatically issue serial numbers when a product is purchased. That means if you sell your own software, or you have purchased the resale rights to other&#8217;s software, you can now use wpStoreCart to not only sell the software, but to automatically issue a serial&#8230; <a class=\"continue_reading\" href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/\">Continue reading &#187;</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"admin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1755:\"<p>With the release of wpStoreCart 2.2.9, you can now have wpStoreCart automatically issue serial numbers when a product is purchased.  That means if you sell your own software, or you have purchased the resale rights to other&#8217;s software, you can now use wpStoreCart to not only sell the software, but to automatically issue a serial number.  This is perfect for software developers and resellers who want to leverage a WordPress ecommerce solution with a minimal amount of work.<br />\n<span id=\"more-658\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\"><img src=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"SERIAL\" width=\"648\" height=\"302\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-659\" /></a></p>\n<p>Use the <strong>Edit Products > Downloads</strong> tab to add serial numbers, as seen in the screenshot above.</p>\n<p>Also included in 2.2.9, is the ability to specify an Orders &#038; Downloads page in General Settings.  This will allow the [downloadurl] in emails and other wpStoreCart functions to know where to tell your users to browse to.</p>\n<p>Speaking of serial numbers and emails, there was a new email added: Email Sent When Issuing Serial Number</p>\n<p>Some of the other changes in 2.2.9 are:<br />\n- Fixed a bug that had caused the emails that were to be sent after an order is approved to fail<br />\n- Added a new tab for product editing: downloads<br />\n- Fixed a bug that caused PayPal donations to be activated when they should not be<br />\n- Added the echoFields() method to the PaymentGateway() class for debugging problems in the payment gateway<br />\n- Started adding a new mode to the cart that uses Cookies instead of Sessions to store the carts contents</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:68:\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL-150x150.png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n			\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:60:\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"SERIAL\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:68:\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL-150x150.png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n	\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"What to Expect From wpStoreCart 2.2.7\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://wpstorecart.com/what-to-expect-from-wpstorecart-2-2-7/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://wpstorecart.com/what-to-expect-from-wpstorecart-2-2-7/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Apr 2011 00:51:31 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://wpstorecart.com/?p=632\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:496:\"We&#8217;ve got a new release coming up soon, and here&#8217;s what to expect in wpStoreCart v2.2.7: Coupons that use a percentage discount Ability to rename advanced variation categories without invalidating previously set prices Ability for customers to sort your products by newest, oldest, lowest price, highest price, most popular Hope to have it out tonight,&#8230; <a class=\"continue_reading\" href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/what-to-expect-from-wpstorecart-2-2-7/\">Continue reading &#187;</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"admin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:430:\"<p>We&#8217;ve got a new release coming up soon, and here&#8217;s what to expect in wpStoreCart v2.2.7:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Coupons that use a percentage discount</li>\n<li>Ability to rename advanced variation categories without invalidating previously set prices</li>\n<li>Ability for customers to sort your products by newest, oldest, lowest price, highest price, most popular</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hope to have it out tonight, or tomorrow.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.