rly Publication. You can read more about the WP Candy Quarterly Publication via Ryan&#8217;s announcement on the WP Candy website . If you&#8217;re a fan of WP Candy [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Dan Milward\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1626:\"<p><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/11/quarterlyannouncement-teaser.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"284\" /></p>\n<p>The other day, my friend Ryan Imel from WP Candy sent me a message letting me know that WP Candy had launched a new site selling pre-orders for their new Quarterly Publication. You can read more about the WP Candy Quarterly Publication via <a href=\"http://wpcandy.com/announces/quarterly-pre-orders\">Ryan&#8217;s announcement</a> on the WP Candy website . If you&#8217;re a fan of WP Candy like I am, then you can cough up your hard earned coins and <a href=\"http://wpcandy.com/quarterly\">pre-order your copy</a> now.</p>\n<p>What I like about the WP Candy Publication is that it gives me something kitsch, interesting and collectable that I can take away from my digital display &#8211; be it my iPhone, iPad or my Macbook. Sometimes, it&#8217;s nice to have a read in the bath, right?</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m pleased to say that the WP Candy Shoppe is powered by the <a title=\"Home of the WordPress e-Commerce Plugin\" href=\"http://www.getshopped.org\">WP e-Commerce Plugin</a>. It is a simple and effective implementation of e-Commerce, the buyer can choose from two different subscription models, either a yearly subscription or one publication at a time, and of course whatever the case may be, the website calculates the shipping costs based on the order and the location of the buyer and then bills the buyer accordingly.</p>\n<p>Interested? The WPCandy Quarterly is immediately <a title=\"The WPCandy Quarterly\" href=\"http://wpcandy.com/quarterly\">available for pre-order</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/showcase-the-wpcandy-quarterly-magazine/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"WP e-Commerce 3.8.7.2 security and bug fix release\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-e-commerce-3-8-7-2-security-and-bug-fix-release/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-e-commerce-3-8-7-2-security-and-bug-fix-release/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 22 Nov 2011 03:26:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lan