b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:363:\"Hi everyone, We&#8217;re very happy to announce that 3.8.7 is finally ready for the public. In our previous beta and release candidate announcements, we introduced several new features in this release: Hierarchical URL: A new setting to allow product sub-categories in permalinks. Claimed stock clearance interval: Users can now set the amount of time stock [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Gary Cao\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2091:\"<p><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"new settings tabs\" src=\"http://getshopped.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/tabs.png  \" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"40\" /></p>\n<p>Hi everyone,</p>\n<p>We&#8217;re very happy to announce that 3.8.7 is finally ready for the public. In our previous <a href=\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-e-commerce-3-8-7-beta/\">beta</a> and <a href=\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-e-commerce-3-8-7-rc1/\">release candidate</a> announcements, we introduced several new features in this release:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hierarchical URL: A new setting to allow product sub-categories in permalinks.</li>\n<li>Claimed stock clearance interval: Users can now set the amount of time stock in cart are reserved.</li>\n<li>Settings page tabs are restyled</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This version also includes 30+ bug fixes, among those are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Discounts / coupons not passing to Paypal gateways.</li>\n<li>Fatal memory allocation error in Add Product page causing the page output to be cut off.</li>\n<li>Product category title is replaced by first product&#8217;s title.</li>\n<li>Saving thumbnail settings caused PHP timeout.</li>\n<li>is_home() is true when viewing default category on products page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Read the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wp-e-commerce/changelog/\">full changelog</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;d like to thank our community members for their contribution to make this release possible: <a href=\"http://www.leewillis.co.uk/\">Lee Willis</a>, <a href=\"http://screamingcodemonkey.com\">Jeffry Ghazally</a>, <a href=\"http://pippinspages.com/\">Pippin Williamson</a>, dlingren, <a href=\"http://www.benhuson.co.uk/\">Ben Huson</a>, groques, Zack Tollman, jRayx. Please keep up the good work!</p>\n<p>As always, before upgrading, make sure you have a <strong>backup of your files and database</strong>. You do it for WordPress. You do it for BuddyPress. Please do it for WP e-Commerce too!</p>\n<p><strong>» <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wp-e-commerce\">Click here to download the latest WP e-Commerce update!</a></strong></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wordpress-e-commerce-3-8-7-official-release/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"16\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"WP e-Commerce 3.8.7-RC1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\"